                        <h3 class="mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4 display-2">
                            <strong>How Artificial Intelligence is Accelerating Drug Discovery</h3></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
